'''李·里德利'''（{{bd|1980年|12月31日|||}}，{{lang|en|Lee Ridley}}）是英国[[棟篤笑|脱口秀喜剧演员]]。他從小已是一位殘疾人士，并且[[啞|无法讲话]]，他是英国首位在脫口秀活动中，使用文字轉換語音的单口喜剧演员，以“失声男孩”（{{lang|en|Lost Voice Guy}}）的艺名演出。 <ref name="JonesIndependent">[https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/comedy/lost-voice-guy-heard-the-one-about-the-standup-comedian-who-cant-speak-9918102.html Lost Voice Guy: Heard the one about the stand-up comedian who can't speak?] {{Wayback|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/comedy/lost-voice-guy-heard-the-one-about-the-standup-comedian-who-cant-speak-9918102.html |date=20150705232640 }}, by Alice Jones, in ''[[the_Independent|the Independent]]''; published 11 December 2014; retrieved 4 July 2015</ref> 他在2018年贏得第12屆[[英国达人|全英一叮]]後走紅。<ref name="RidleyBGT">{{Cite web|title=Britain's Got Talent winner: Lost Voice Guy crowned 2018 champion|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/stayingin/tvfilm/britains-got-talent-2018-lost-voice-guy-crowned-series-12-winner-a3854116.html|accessdate=4 June 2018|author=Natasha Sporn|date=4 June 2018|work=Standard.co.uk|archive-date=2020-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623072204/https://www.standard.co.uk/stayingin/tvfilm/britains-got-talent-2018-lost-voice-guy-crowned-series-12-winner-a3854116.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
=== 早期生活 ===
李·里德利出生於[[達勒姆郡|达勒姆郡]][[康斯特|康斯特]]。在六个月大的时候，他被诊断出患有[[腦性麻痺|腦性麻痺]]。亦因脑部感染，他昏迷了两个月，这影响了他的动作，亦導致他[[啞|无法说话]]。 <ref name="JonesIndependent">[https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/comedy/lost-voice-guy-heard-the-one-about-the-standup-comedian-who-cant-speak-9918102.html Lost Voice Guy: Heard the one about the stand-up comedian who can't speak?], by Alice Jones, in ''[[the_Independent|the Independent]]''; published 11 December 2014; retrieved 4 July 2015</ref><ref name="GraunEvans">[https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2012/jun/06/silent-comedian-lee-ridley-ipad Lee Ridley: making comedy out of silence] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2012/jun/06/silent-comedian-lee-ridley-ipad |date=20210309191606 }}, by Gary Evans, in ''[[the_Guardian|the Guardian]]''; published 6 June 2012; retrieved 4 July 2015</ref>童年時因残障使他难以与人交流，直到八岁时，他才收到了第一台[[语音合成|文字轉換語音]]设备。他在残疾儿童学校的學習得到了老师的支持和帮助。在1999年至2002年之间，他在[[中央兰开夏大学|中央兰开夏大学]]修讀新聞學位及網上新聞學位，<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.lep.co.uk/news/education/former-preston-student-lee-ridley-through-to-the-next-round-of-britain-s-got-talent-1-9129001|title=Former Preston student Lee Ridley through to the next round of Britain's Got Talent|accessdate=23 April 2018|language=en|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612140605/https://www.lep.co.uk/news/education/former-preston-student-lee-ridley-through-to-the-next-round-of-britain-s-got-talent-1-9129001|dead-url=no}}</ref>在前者获得了學士学位，而在后者获得了硕士学位。 2006年，他在BBC和当地报報章担任记者<ref>{{Citation|last=CM Admin|title="Finding My Voice" – Lee Ridley|date=20 November 2012|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-tlLNZVIZjQ|access-date=23 April 2018|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731033634/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-tlLNZVIZjQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然后在2007年担任[[桑德兰|桑德兰]]市的網上文章经理。 <ref name="GraunMOH">[https://www.theguardian.com/society/2015/apr/15/lee-ridley-bbc-new-comedy-award-2014-disabled-cerebral-palsy Lee Ridley: ‘Disabled people are either inspirational, or benefit cheats’] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2015/apr/15/lee-ridley-bbc-new-comedy-award-2014-disabled-cerebral-palsy |date=20200622045947 }}, by Mary O'Hara, at ''[[the_Guardian|the Guardian]]''; published 15 April 2015; retrieved 4 July 2015</ref>

=== 职业 ===
李·里德利从2012年开始表演喜剧。<ref name="PatersonBBC">[https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-17699744 The stand-up comic who cannot speak] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-17699744 |date=20160423150145 }}, by Colin Paterson; at the [[BBC|BBC]]; published 13 April 2012; retrieved 4 July 2015; "two months ago he did his first show"</ref>在觀看罗斯·诺布尔（ Ross Noble）主持的演出之后，他決定成為一位脫口秀演員。在诺布尔模仿[[史蒂芬·霍金|斯蒂芬·霍金]]後，他向诺布尔提出挑战， 声称自己能可以更好地模仿和乔装霍金。为了挑戰，李·里德利购买了一个名为Speak It！的[[iPad|iPad]][[語音產生裝置|语音合成器]]应用程序，亦根据自己的先前構思的句子进行了预先编程。 <ref name="MawsonBBC">[https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-tyne-19179921 Lee Ridley: Stand-up success for 'Lost Voice Guy' comic] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-tyne-19179921 |date=20180613092108 }}, by Phil Mawson, at the [[BBC|BBC]]; published 9 August 2012; retrieved 4 July 2015</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=BBC – The Ouch! Blog: Lee Ridley aka Lost Voice Guy: the communication revolution (technology and disabled people series)|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/ouch/2012/11/lee_ridley_aka_lost_voice_guy.html|accessdate=23 April 2018|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622083418/https://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/ouch/2012/11/lee_ridley_aka_lost_voice_guy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>首次演出后，李·里德利选择能引起观众反响的素材来進行表演，并采用即兴创作的风格，偶尔他会通过語音工具在舞台上即時制作新素材。 <ref name="GraunEvans">[https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2012/jun/06/silent-comedian-lee-ridley-ipad Lee Ridley: making comedy out of silence], by Gary Evans, in ''[[the_Guardian|the Guardian]]''; published 6 June 2012; retrieved 4 July 2015</ref>在2013年的[[愛丁堡國際藝穗節|愛丁堡國際藝穗節]]上成功演出他的第一个表演，但在患上[[肺炎|肺炎]]后，他被迫缩短了[[愛丁堡國際藝穗節|演出]]时间。<ref name="SunderlandEcho">[http://www.sunderlandecho.com/what-s-on/voiceless-comedian-in-hospital-after-contracting-pneumonia-during-edinburgh-fringe-performances-1-5988635 Voiceless comedian in hospital after contracting pneumonia during Edinburgh Fringe performances] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sunderlandecho.com/what-s-on/voiceless-comedian-in-hospital-after-contracting-pneumonia-during-edinburgh-fringe-performances-1-5988635 |date=20160304045457 }}, by Jane O'Neill, in the ''Sunderland Echo''; published 27 August 2013; retrieved 4 July 2015</ref>

2014年，李·里德利赢得了BBC广播电台新喜剧奖<ref name="Award">[http://www.comedy.co.uk/news/story/000001677/lost_voice_guy_wins_new_comedy_award_2014 Lost Voice Guy wins BBC New Comedy Award 2014] {{Wayback|url=http://www.comedy.co.uk/news/story/000001677/lost_voice_guy_wins_new_comedy_award_2014 |date=20150924035349 }}, at British Comedy Guide; published 17 December 2014</ref>，到2015年，他开始投入专业喜剧事业， <ref name="Giggle">[http://www.gigglebeats.co.uk/2015/06/bbc-launches-its-2015-radio-new-comedy-award/ BBC launches its 2015 New Comedy Award] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gigglebeats.co.uk/2015/06/bbc-launches-its-2015-radio-new-comedy-award/ |date=20160304042324 }}, by Andrew Dipper; at GiggleBeats; published 17 June 2015; retrieved 5 July 2015</ref>亦参加了当年愛丁堡國際藝穗節的一场名为《愚蠢的残障人士》的新节目。次年，他表演了该节目的续集，名为“第2集”，并于2017年推出了一个名为"Inspiration Porn"的新节目，该节目為取笑有关残疾人士的令人「鼓舞人心」的影片和迷因。<ref name="TWR170715">{{Cite web|title=Interview: Lost Voice Guy|url=http://theweereview.com/interview/lost-voice-guy/|accessdate=4 June 2018|author=Peacock|date=21 April 2018|first=Robert|publisher=The Wee Review|archive-date=2020-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623071642/https://theweereview.com/interview/lost-voice-guy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>获奖后， [https://www.thesequaltrust.org.uk/meet-the-team The Sequal Trust] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thesequaltrust.org.uk/meet-the-team |date=20210217115052 }}与他联系，The Sequal Trust希望李·里德利成為他们有關沟通障碍的慈善机构的贊助人，而目前仍保持这一头衔。

在2018年，李·里德利担任[[BBC廣播四台|BBC廣播四台]][[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]"Ability"的主角，他与作家兼喜剧演员Katherine Jakeways （第一和第二輯）以及Kat Butterfield和Daniel Audritt（第三輯）共同撰写了此剧。 <ref name="TWR170715">{{Cite web|title=Interview: Lost Voice Guy|url=http://theweereview.com/interview/lost-voice-guy/|accessdate=4 June 2018|author=Peacock|date=21 April 2018|first=Robert|publisher=[[The_Wee_Review|The Wee Review]]}}</ref>他的角色為扮演残疾人士的“Matt”，故事主要內容為Matt从父母的家搬出，与他最好的朋友在学校读书，有別於Matt的父母，他的朋友則以正常人來對待他。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/whats-on/comedy-news/lost-voice-guy-lee-ridley-12415474|title=Lost Voice Guy Lee Ridley stars in new BBC Radio 4 sitcom|author=Hodgson|first=Barbara|date=6 January 2017|work=nechronicle|accessdate=23 April 2018|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120003945/https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/whats-on/comedy-news/lost-voice-guy-lee-ridley-12415474|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Ability - Radio 4 Sitcom|url=https://www.comedy.co.uk/radio/ability/|author=Guide|first=British Comedy|work=British Comedy Guide|access-date=2021-02-18|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023021325/https://www.comedy.co.uk/radio/ability/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2018年6月，李·里德利參加了全英一叮，成功通过了初賽阶段，并進入了總決賽，获得了觀眾投票的第一名，从而赢得了英国第12届的《[[全英一叮|全英一叮]]》。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Britain's Got Talent's The Lost Voice Guy has everyone in stitches|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/britains-got-talent/news/a855342/britains-got-talent-lost-voice-guy/|accessdate=21 April 2018|author=Hegarty|date=21 April 2018|first=Tasha|publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|archive-date=2018-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181110163318/http://www.digitalspy.com/tv/britains-got-talent/news/a855342/britains-got-talent-lost-voice-guy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="RidleyBGT">{{Cite web|title=Britain's Got Talent winner: Lost Voice Guy crowned 2018 champion|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/stayingin/tvfilm/britains-got-talent-2018-lost-voice-guy-crowned-series-12-winner-a3854116.html|accessdate=4 June 2018|author=Natasha Sporn|date=4 June 2018|work=Standard.co.uk}}</ref> <ref name="Chortle 4 June 2018">{{Cite web|title=Revealed: Just how clear was Lost Voice Guy's victory|url=http://www.chortle.co.uk/news/2018/06/04/40131/revealed%3A_just_how_clear_was_lost_voice_guys_victory|accessdate=4 June 2018|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|date=4 June 2018|work=www.chortle.co.uk|publisher=Chortle|archive-date=2020-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625023852/https://www.chortle.co.uk/news/2018/06/04/40131/revealed:_just_how_clear_was_lost_voice_guys_victory|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2019年2月，李·里德利出演了[[英國廣播公司第三台|英國廣播公司第三台]]的电视连续剧《Jerk》。

在2019年，李·里德利参加了《全美一叮：冠軍戰》<ref>{{Cite web|title=America’s Got Talent: 9 comedians return for Champions season – ComedyNews.Org :: Comedy News Organization :: CN.O|url=https://comedynews.org/2019/01/14/americas-got-talent-9-comedians-return-for-champions-season/|accessdate=2020-07-12|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123035713/https://comedynews.org/2019/01/14/americas-got-talent-9-comedians-return-for-champions-season/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Lost Voice Guy honoured sharing stage with Susan Boyle on AGT: The Champions|url=https://metro.co.uk/2019/01/24/lost-voice-guy-honoured-share-stage-susan-boyle-go-war-americas-got-talent-champions-8381664/|accessdate=2020-07-12|date=2019-01-24|work=Metro|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712161957/https://metro.co.uk/2019/01/24/lost-voice-guy-honoured-share-stage-susan-boyle-go-war-americas-got-talent-champions-8381664/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，但在初賽中被淘汰。同年，他还发行了他的第一本书“I'm Only In It For The Parking”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Lee Ridley to release Lost Voice Guy book in 2019|url=https://www.comedy.co.uk/shop/news/3205/lost_voice_guy_book/|accessdate=2020-07-12|author=Guide|date=2018-07-28|first=British Comedy|work=British Comedy Guide|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712161958/https://www.comedy.co.uk/shop/news/3205/lost_voice_guy_book/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Transworld wins Lost Voice Guy's first book {{!}} The Bookseller|url=https://www.thebookseller.com/news/transworld-wins-britain-s-got-talent-winner-lee-ridleys-first-book-839091|accessdate=2020-07-12|work=www.thebookseller.com|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712161955/https://www.thebookseller.com/news/transworld-wins-britain-s-got-talent-winner-lee-ridleys-first-book-839091|dead-url=no}}</ref>

